### Create a new book
POST http://localhost:3000/books HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "test3",
  "img": "image3"
}

### List all books 
GET http://localhost:3000/books HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Delete a particular book
DELETE http://localhost:3000/1aa7 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json